{"tid":2400954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港增21宗本地確診　張竹君籲市民農曆新年減少聚餐","createTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T11:05:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7502f44c57b116a5e1bcfb2b47f20e4073c78d","tid":2400954,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574954-20210209.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574954-20210209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=faa5d247\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574954-20210209.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a4c23c3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574954-20210209.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增26宗新型肺炎確診個案，本地個案佔21宗，其中5宗感染源頭不明，初步確診個案大約20宗。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘安泰邨保良局安泰復康中心1名院友確診，數十名院友和工作人員需要檢疫；1名曾經在九龍佐治五世公園和深水埗流連的無家者確診。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君再次提醒市民，農曆新年期間減少聚餐等活動。"},{"pid":"d0d89a920f881643484ce1ffbb961458b2b45ca2","tid":2400954,"uid":14983,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"君君同老公仔聚餐"},{"pid":"f1ffe910593de4b14445c23843b6257fb81e0fb0","tid":2400954,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"好人好姐點會中"},{"pid":"fc62ef6995b81d62e7b907958930ca506a14ef33","tid":2400954,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d89a920f881643484ce1ffbb961458b2b45ca2","tid":2400954,"uid":14983,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:52:47.000Z","msg":"君君同老公仔聚餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"君君知唔知年初一邊度有元寶臘燭香買"},{"pid":"74d13fdddd04cfe9b3d418b6c327e3d97fe8c078","tid":2400954,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T1